Name: Average time from 'SW-Checklist Completed' to 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Total time from 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' to 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Minimum time from 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' to 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Average time between 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total resolution time of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to the 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' after 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Minimum time it takes 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' to be followed by 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Average time for 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' to lead to a decision ('SW-EIC Reject', 'SW-EIC Major Revision', 'SW-EIC Minor Revision', 'SW-EIC Accept')
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': "activity == 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'", 'end': "activity == 'SW-EIC Reject' or activity == 'SW-EIC Major Revision' or activity == 'SW-EIC Minor Revision' or activity == 'SW-EIC Accept'", 'aggregation': 'average', 'filter': '', 'group_by': ''}

Name: Total time for all instances of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-Awaiting AE Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' to 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision' for papers that required major revisions
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Total time from 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' to 'SW-EIC Major Revision'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' for papers that were accepted ('SW-EIC Accept')
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Average time from 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' to 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Total time from 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' to 'SW-Reviewer Agreed' for all variants where this transition occurs
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Minimum time from 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' to 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers Challenge Paper' for papers that underwent a challenge paper review process
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers Challenge Paper'
